Dataset of surface reactions for gwb programs
Dataset format: sep22
Surface type: IonEx_IGCSM
Model type: ion-exchange  gaines-thomas
Surface potential: n/a
Surface capacitance: n/a
Thermo dataset: PSINagra2020v1-5.tdat
* The ClaySor 2023 Sorption Thermodynamic Databse of 2 SPNE SC/CE Sorption Model for Illite and Montmorillonite  
* 
* transferred into GWB format from the PHREEQC file claysor23_v0.7.dat by Dr. Frank Bok (HZDR) f.bok@hzdr.de
* Note that the user sets the exchange capacity (CEC) from the command line with the "exchange_capacity" command or
* within the GUI sub-menu "Sorbing Surfaces".
* 
* The database is consistent and shold be used for GWB calculations with the PSI/Nagra 
* TDB 2020 (Hummel & Thoenen 2023) aqueous thermodynamic database http://www.psi.ch/les/database, see "Thermo dataset" above
* 
* Database of reactions generated using ThermoMatch reactions generator tool. 
* Reactions exported to phreeqc format using ThermoMatch export functionality.
* https://thermohub.org/thermomatch. For questions G. Dan Miron dan.miron@psi.ch
* 
* Change history
* 25 Nov. 2024 first release v0.1 
